    "Specifically, we track instances where LLM chatbots generate responses for corresponding prohibited scenarios.To evaluate the overall jailbreak success rate, we introduce the metric of query success rate, which is defined as follows:Q = S TTABLE V: Performance comparison of each baseline in generating jailbreak prompts in terms of query success rate.",
