    "This metric helps in understanding how often our strategies can trick the model into generating prohibited content.",
    "Further, to evaluate the quality of the generated jailbreak prompts, we define the jailbreak prompt success rate as below:J = G PWhere G is the number of generated jailbreak prompts with at least one successful query and P is the total number of generated jailbreak prompts.",
